query:
SELECT s.id, s.siteNumber, s.pricePerDay, s.weekendPricePerDay, s.pricePerWeek, c.name as centreName
FROM sites s
JOIN shopping_centres c ON s.centreId = c.id
WHERE c.name LIKE '%Chullora%'
ORDER BY s.siteNumber;
